我们以前听过这个。

138
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:54,960
So why don't we hear some examples to help you understand how it's used.
那我们听一些例子，帮助你理解怎么用。

139
00:04:54,960 --> 00:04:55,960
Example one.
例子一。

140
00:04:55,960 --> 00:04:56,960
Hurry up.
快点。

141
