Thanks for letting me crash here tonight.
谢谢你今晚让我借宿。

163
00:05:59,600 --> 00:06:02,440
It's no problem, brother.
没问题，兄弟。

164
00:06:02,440 --> 00:06:07,640
I wanted a pad where people could come, listen to music, and just hang loose.
我想要一个地方，人们可以来听音乐，放松自在。

165
00:06:07,640 --> 00:06:09,040
You dig what I'm saying?
你明白我的意思吗？

166
00:06:09,040 --> 00:06:10,600
I dig it, man.
我明白，老兄。

167
00:06:10,600 --> 00:06:13,680
We could throw a bash here and make it a really happening scene.
我们可以在这儿办个派对，让它成为一个热闹的场面。

168
00:06:13,680 --> 00:06:14,760
Yeah, man.
是啊，老兄。

169
00:06:14,760 --> 00:06:16,520
That would be groovy.
那会很棒的。

170
00:06:16,520 --> 00:06:18,960
Hey, I got to split for a while.
嘿，我得离开一会儿。

171
00:06:18,960 --> 00:06:21,040
Are you okay here by yourself?
你一个人在这儿没问题吧？

172
00:06:21,040 --> 00:06:22,600
Don't worry about me, brother.
别担心我，兄弟。

173
00:06:22,600 --> 00:06:24,520
You go take care of your business.
你去忙你的事吧。

174
00:06:24,520 --> 00:06:25,520
All right.
好的。

175
00:06:25,520 --> 00:06:26,520
Peace out.
再见。

176
00:06:26,520 --> 00:06:27,520
All right.
好的。

