179
00:06:41,760 --> 00:06:42,760
Putting it together.
整合。

180
00:06:42,760 --> 00:06:43,760
All right.
好的。

181
00:06:43,760 --> 00:06:46,400
I'm putting it together today.
今天我来整合。

