He said, you go take care of business.
他说，你去处理你的事。

269
00:09:32,760 --> 00:09:34,080
You take care of business.
你处理你的事。

270
00:09:34,080 --> 00:09:35,080
Okay.
好的。

271
00:09:35,080 --> 00:09:37,480
So I have to take care of business.
所以我得处理我的事。

272
00:09:37,480 --> 00:09:40,920
So we're not really talking about business and work here, are we?
但我们这里不是真的在说生意和工作，对吧？

273
00:09:40,920 --> 00:09:41,920
No, no, no.
不，不，不。

274
00:09:41,920 --> 00:09:46,440
So basically what we're saying is, go handle your affairs.
所以基本上我们说的是，去处理你的事情。

275
00:09:46,440 --> 00:09:49,400
So do the things you have to do.
就是做你必须做的事。

276
00:09:49,400 --> 00:09:50,400
Okay.
好的。

