00:10:35,640 --> 00:10:38,240
Yeah, man, that would be groovy.
是啊，老兄，那会很棒的。

296
00:10:38,240 --> 00:10:40,480
Hey, I got to split for a while.
嘿，我得先走一会儿。

297
00:10:40,480 --> 00:10:42,320
Are you okay here by yourself?
你一个人在这儿行吗？

