Don't worry about me, brother.
别担心我，兄弟。

299
00:10:43,320 --> 00:10:46,320
You go take care of your business.
你去处理你的事吧。

300
00:10:46,320 --> 00:10:48,320
All right.
好的。

301
00:10:48,320 --> 00:10:50,320
Peace out.
再见。

302
00:10:50,320 --> 00:10:51,760
All right.
好的。

